{"tid":1835872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[毋忘沙士血的教訓] 要封關口，停市，全民大清潔運動","createTime":"2020-01-23T04:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:15:44.000Z","uid":237425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5c39fa086af73ffaef043e265a611ff03a911e42","tid":1835872,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"今次根本係威力勁撚過沙士<br />\n潛伏期長<br />\n可以冇發燒既確診<br />\n*今朝有消息仲話眼睛感染而中招<br />\n<br />\n關口一撚定要封<br />\n知道響支那黎既人就請佢走<br />\n<br />\n香港境內支那人即刻送去隔離營觀察2星期以上先<br />\n<br />\n咪撚開工啦，通勤坐車番office9成9交叉感染<br />\n<br />\n周圍都要狂清洗，洗地，抹完再抹<br />\n個人用品除左口罩<br />\n手套同護目鏡都應該要<br />\n必要時要用d用幾次就丟既防護衫"},{"pid":"6792feb450dd9bd117ab0cae164f676191cfc6de","tid":1835872,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302a6bbeda8039e948040a1ddf2e0143e6a998d5","tid":1835872,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}